      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Chiefly letters of prominent 19th century Virginians: John
         Randolph (1812); Andrew Jackson (1830); John Marshall (1831);
         Edwin Henry Landseer (1845); John C. Calhoun (1849); Edwin
         Henry Landseer (1851); Charles Dickens (1858); William Cabell
         Rives (1861); John Letcher (1862); Jefferson Davis (1864); J.
         E. B. Stuart (1864); Alexander H. H. Stuart (1866); John
         Letcher (1866); Gilbert C. Walker (1872); Joseph E. Johnston
         (1881); Fred W. M. Holliday (1881)</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement>
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is arranged chronologically.</p>
      </arrangement>
